2000-08-23  Gary Thomas  <gthomas@redhat.com>

	* src/load.c (do_load): Use paramterized command line parser.

	* include/redboot.h: 
	* src/main.c (scan_opts): Better support for simple flags.

	* src/flash.c: Add "-l" (list only) option to 'fconfig'.

